text: [Jhanak SPOILER Alert! Jhanak swears to ruin Arshi and Anirudh's lives as they caused her great suffering ](/spoiler-alert/jhanak-spoiler-alert-jhanak-swears-ruin-arshi-and-anirudhs-lives-they-caused-her) [TellychakkarTeam](/users/tellychakkarteam)on Fri, 08/30/2024 - 11:47 MUMBAI: Star Plus’ latest show, 'Jhanak', features Hiba Nawab in the titular role of Jhanak, Krushal Ahuja as Anirudh, and Chandani Sharma as Arshi. This enthralling series promises to captivate audiences with its intense storyline. The viewers are drawn into the gripping narrative, ensuring an exhilarating and unforgettable viewing experience. The compelling twist in the storyline promises to keep audiences on the edge of their seats, captivated by the unfolding drama and eager to see how these pivotal moments will shape the characters' fates. The current track concentrates on Jhanak's efforts to help Anirudh to recover quickly by taking care of him. However, he is unaware that Jhanak is his caretaker. Also Read- [Jhanak Spoiler: Bose Family stands shocked as Anirudh loves Jhanak](https://www.tellychakkar.com/spoiler-alert/jhanak-spoiler-bose-family-stands-shocked-anirudh-loves-jhanak-240623) It appears that Jhanak, who purports to be carrying Anirudh's child, would cause Arshi and Anirudh to have restless nights. Arshi is aware that Anirudh may be the father of Jhanak's unborn child, even though Anirudh will insist he had nothing to do with Jhanak's pregnancy. As she is determined to give her child Anirudh's name because she doesn't want them to go through what she did in life—having her father reject her mother—Jhanak will be shown residing in Bose House. As Arshi becomes irritated, she pushes Jhanak, who is pregnant, off the stairwell, resulting in her miscarriage. Jhanak will appear to be inconsolable as Arshi stole her most valuable possession. Jhanak will be perceived as broken, and she swears to ruin Arshi and Anirudh's lives because they caused her great suffering.
